==============================================================
ShapeBM Interactive GUI
--------------------------------------------------------------
'The Shape Boltzmann Machine: a Strong Model of Object Shape'
S. M. Ali Eslami, Nicolas Heess and John Winn
Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR) 2012
==============================================================

- Run script start_gui.m in MATLAB to start the GUI.
- See video in the supplementary material for a walkthrough.
- Edit gui/gui_settings_horses.m and gui/gui_settings_motorbikes.m to change Gibbs sampling settings.
- The GUI may be slightly sluggish on older hardware.
- Tested to work with MATLAB R2009b+ on Windows/OS X/Linux. 
